text: Mohammad Reza Mohajeri () is an Iranian football manager. He is currently head coach of Mes Kerman. Mohajeri started his coaching career in Shirin Faraz in 2011. == Honours == ===Manager honours=== ;Siah Jamegan *Azadegan League (1): 2014–15 *Azadegan League (Runner-up Group A) (1): 2013–14 *Second Division (1): 2012–13 ==References== Category:Living people Category:Iranian football managers Category:1964 births Category:Shahr Khodro F.C. managers
